general.description: The PZL.37 Los is the dedicated twin-engined bomber of OCP. It can carry up to 8 bombs at once, bringing devastation upon anything in its sights. You can even install additional racks in the center of the plane for extra bombs! Three onboard machine-guns protect its hull from enemy aircraft at every angle, although you'll need a crew to operate those... The PZL.37 Los is the best choice if you're looking to 'adjust' villager population (and prices).
